            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
                <div class="text-3xl mb-4" aria-hidden="true">🚚</div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">We Transport</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Our expert movers handle your goods with care and deliver them on time.</p>
            </div>
